sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 로그인 회원
    participant JSP as detail.jsp
    participant C as CommunityPostController
    participant CS as CommunityCommentServiceImpl
    participant CM as CommunityCommentMapper
    participant DB as Oracle

    Note over User,DB: 조회 - 상세 페이지
    User->>JSP: GET /community/detail?id=
    JSP->>C: detail(id)
    C->>CS: getCommentList(postId)
    CS->>CM: selectCommentList PARENT_ID IS NULL
    CM->>DB: SELECT 최상위 댓글
    CS->>CM: selectRepliesByPostId
    CM->>DB: SELECT 대댓글
    CS->>CS: parentMap에 replies 묶기
    C-->>JSP: comments 트리 구조

    Note over User,DB: 등록 - 답글
    User->>JSP: 답글 입력
    JSP->>C: POST /community/comment parentId
    C->>CS: insertComment
    CS->>CS: validateParentComment
    CS->>CM: INSERT PARENT_ID
    CM->>DB: INSERT TB_POST_COMMENT
